<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://eis.bris.ac.uk/~plcdib/imprints/vanparijsinterview.html" class="external text" title="http://eis.bris.ac.uk/~plcdib/imprints/vanparijsinterview.html" rel="nofollow">Interview with Philippe van Parijs</a></li>
